Invocation Name: sergeant will radio
des: Sergeant Will's Radio broadcasts History As It Happened. Listen to news & entertainment originally filling the airwaves during the current month in the 1940s through the 1980s. Escape into Golden Age Radio during the day with darker thrills in the evening. Night Beat & CBS Radio Mystery Theater on the air nightly. WW2 news reports hourly.
